
I. Lighting
 A. Books
  1. Game Engine Architecture
   i. p 427, 10.1.3.2 The Pong Lighting Model
    ii. equation on p 428
     iii. lightIntensity = surfaceAmbianceReflectance * ambiantLightIntensity +
     				for (each light source){
     					diffuseReflectivity * DotProduct(surfaceNormal, vertexToLight) + 
     					specularReflectivity * DotProduct(reflectedVertexToLight, vertexToCamera) /\ surfaceSpecularGlossiness
     					* lightColorIntensity
     				}
     		with reflectedVertexToLight = surfaceNormal scaled by (2 * DotProduct(surfaceNormal, vertexToLight))
     						- vertexToLight
